## Limitations

This report is based on available literature and expert opinions, which may not encompass all perspectives on the topic. The findings are subject to the biases inherent in the sources used. Additionally, the impact of competition can vary significantly based on individual child characteristics and the specific context in which competition occurs. Further empirical research could provide more definitive conclusions.